commitResults.messageTitle: Changed chatbot name + Implement skeleton version
Echo function: make bot repeat user input
commitResults.messageBody: Allows bot to echo commands entered by the user, and exits when the user types the command "bye".

commitResults.messageTitle: Add and List function: bot is able to store and repeat user input
commitResults.messageBody: Allows bot the ability to store whatever text entered by the user and display them back to the user when requested.

commitResults.messageTitle: Mark as done function: bot is able to mark task as done to keep track of progress
commitResults.messageBody: Allows bot the ability to mark tasks as done, as well as the ability to change the status back to not done.

commitResults.messageTitle: ToDos, Dealines and Events function: Bot is able to take in and create todo, dealine and event tasks
commitResults.messageBody: Keeps track of total number of tasks, created a parser to take in command inputs, takes in differernt task types.

commitResults.messageTitle: Text-ui test function: Automated UI test
commitResults.messageBody: Created some commands for automated UI testing.

commitResults.messageTitle: Exception function: bot is able to throw exceptions when inout is invalid
commitResults.messageBody: Allows bot to throw simple exceptions when input is invalid
